{"tid":1082682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住客掟煙頭燒衫釀火災 250人疏散","createTime":"2019-03-29T06:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T07:14:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e0d184961027231354d0f20c782ec2251e5e4f2","tid":1082682,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190329/20644042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F20644042&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=b206fe6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190329%2F20644042&h=feaebc2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190329/20644042</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住客掟煙頭燒衫釀火災 250人疏散<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190329/large/29la8p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190329%2Flarge%2F29la8p06.jpg&h=555b2a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批居民疏散到地下安全地方。黃江奇攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】東涌逸東邨一個曾多次投訴被人高空拋擲煙頭燒毀衣服的單位，昨凌晨晾曬的衣服又被高處擲下的煙頭燒着並釀成大火，南亞裔一家四口驚醒及時逃生幸無受傷，但家園盡毀，一家人事後要房署安排臨時住所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190329/large/a1004a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190329%2Flarge%2Fa1004a.gif&h=984af22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東涌逸東邨火警，起火單位火光熊熊。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n火警中，75歲姓李老婦感不適送院治理，另一名7歲男童及兩男一女（31至33歲）感不適，事後自行到醫院求醫，約250人疏散到地下安全地方。現場為悅逸樓15樓一單位，住有南亞夫婦及兩兒子，戶主阿Butt在尖沙嘴工作。據他說入住15年來多次被人高空擲物，每月有一至兩次煙頭燒爛衣服事件，但多次向房署投訴都沒有改善。<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨3時許，Butt單位外牆晾衫架衣物着火，並蔓延入屋內，街坊發現報警；當時Butt與家人熟睡中，有人透過對講機通知他，他未及穿衣即喚醒家人逃生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主失工作服無法上班<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場約半小時將火救熄，全屋遭嚴重焚毀。Butt一家並無受傷，但他因失去工作服無法上班，身上衣服也是鄰居所送，兩子亦因失去校服昨日沒有上學。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n麗翠苑最貴306萬單位 一小時內被揀<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n賣電器無回收舊機 實惠先施罰款"},{"pid":"28821b7df414e9ed7627826e0d6802bf597a6ee7","tid":1082682,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"我屋企個廁所都有人掟煙頭入黎 <br />\n煙鏟真係好仆街"},{"pid":"8cfe3e149c2862f66798c07c7dbc203d8a034b35","tid":1082682,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da36642cd2cd1bfc1a484072d7fb9873eea4bbf3","tid":1082682,"uid":280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"屌⋯⋯掟落廁所好難咩 <br />\n係要飛出街<br />\n係街食完都周圍彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c95548fb49f9b64060941df409a9124f46c435","tid":1082682,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da36642cd2cd1bfc1a484072d7fb9873eea4bbf3","tid":1082682,"uid":280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"屌⋯⋯掟落廁所好難咩 <br />\n係要飛出街<br />\n係街食完都周圍彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"其實掟落廁所好似沖唔走<br />\n最好都係整熄佢然後揼落垃圾桶"},{"pid":"6a06e2203d4f6a2d7cf82645db66e71a95f5bb6e","tid":1082682,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"食煙已經夠仆街<br />\n仲要掉落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee4d4c05e18a7d858614be9503ce14e48fe910b","tid":1082682,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07: